cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with text sentiment analysis and text classification, which are core topics in computational linguistics (CL) and information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new technique for text classification using machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed model on different text mining algorithms, which can be related to the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
